            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1659.-step-4-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Cook the coppa </strong></p>\n<p>Add the <strong>sliced</strong> <strong>coppa</strong> to a baking tray and put the tray in the oven for 6-8 minutes or until crispy.</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
